        <h1>Recession Indicators Dashboard 2026</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Real-time tracking of 8 leading economic indicators to gauge the probability of a US recession. Data is dynamically updated and compared against historical recession triggers.</p>

        <div class="grid-stats">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Yield Curve (10Y-2Y)</h3>
